---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Montessori School Melkbos: What Makes Lily House Unique — Lily House">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="breadcrumb"><a href="/blog" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);">← Back to Blog</a></p>
      <h1>Montessori School Melkbos: What Makes Lily House Unique on the West Coast</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">April 28, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:720px;">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580582932707-520aed937b7b?w=1200&q=80" alt="Melkbos campus" style="width:100%;border-radius:1rem;margin-bottom:2rem;" />
      <p>Nestled along the stunning West Coast, Lily House Melkbos offers a unique Montessori education that blends coastal charm with academic excellence.</p>
      <h2 style="color:var(--teal);margin:1.5rem 0 1rem;">What Sets Lily House Melkbos Apart</h2>
      <ul style="color:var(--text-light);line-height:1.8;">
        <li><strong>Small class sizes</strong> — every child receives individualised attention</li>
        <li><strong>Experienced Montessori guides</strong> — led by Jess Hanafey</li>
        <li><strong>Coastal learning environment</strong> — deep connection with nature</li>
        <li><strong>Pre-primary and primary programmes</strong> — 18 months through 9 years</li>
      </ul>
      <div style="text-align:center;margin-top:2rem;">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-teal">Book a Tour</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
